# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "Linear"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid ""
"Interpolated values are calculated linear (each step value is equal). Icon: :"
"guilabel:`Diamond`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai interpolasi dihitung secara linear (setiap nilai langkah sama). Ikon: :"
"guilabel:`Diamond`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid "Constant"
msgstr "Konstan"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Interpolated values stay the same until the next key frame, and jump to the "
"new value. Icon: :guilabel:`Square`."
msgstr ""
"Nilai interpolasi tetap sama sampai key frame berikutnya, dan melompat ke "
"nilai baru. Ikon: :guilabel:`Square`."

