# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:77
msgid "Timing"
msgstr "Pengaturan Waktu"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:78
msgid ""
"Changing how fast a clip plays is done with the :guilabel:`Time` property "
"and the :guilabel:`Timing` tool."
msgstr ""
"Mengubah kecepatan pemutaran klip dilakukan dengan properti :guilabel:`Time` "
"dan alat :guilabel:`Timing`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:80
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Time` menu offers presets such as normal, fast, slow, freeze, "
"and reverse. See details in :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Menu :guilabel:`Time` menawarkan preset seperti normal, cepat, lambat, beku, "
"dan balik. Lihat detail di :ref:`clip_time_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:81
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timing` tool lets you drag a clip’s edges to speed it up or "
"slow it down. OpenShot adds the needed Time keyframes and **scales your "
"other keyframes** so your animations stay aligned. Shorter clips play "
"faster, longer clips play slower. See more: :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Alat :guilabel:`Timing` memungkinkan Anda menyeret tepi klip untuk "
"mempercepat atau memperlambatnya. OpenShot menambahkan keyframe Time yang "
"diperlukan dan **mengatur skala keyframe lain** sehingga animasi Anda tetap "
"selaras. Klip yang lebih pendek diputar lebih cepat, klip yang lebih panjang "
"diputar lebih lambat. Lihat lebih lanjut: :ref:`clip_time_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:86
msgid "Repeating"
msgstr "Pengulangan"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:87
msgid ""
"To play a clip multiple times, use :guilabel:`Right-Click → Time → Repeat`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memutar klip beberapa kali, gunakan :guilabel:`Klik Kanan → Time → "
"Repeat`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:89
msgid ":guilabel:`Loop` repeats in one direction (forward or reverse)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Loop` mengulang dalam satu arah (maju atau mundur)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ping-Pong` alternates direction (forward then backward, etc.)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ping-Pong` bergantian arah (maju lalu mundur, dll.)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom` can add a short pause between passes, speed up or slow "
"down each pass, including keyframes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Custom` dapat menambahkan jeda singkat antar putaran, mempercepat "
"atau memperlambat setiap putaran, termasuk keyframe."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:93
msgid ""
"OpenShot writes the :guilabel:`Time` curve for you, and you can edit those "
"keyframes just like any other. See more: :ref:`clip_time_repeat_ref`."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot menulis kurva :guilabel:`Time` untuk Anda, dan Anda dapat mengedit "
"keyframe tersebut seperti biasa. Lihat lebih lanjut: :ref:"
"`clip_time_repeat_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:97
msgid "Bézier Presets"
msgstr "Preset Bézier"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:98
msgid ""
"When using a Bézier curve for animation, OpenShot includes more than 20 "
"curve presets (which affect the shape of the curve). For example, **Ease-"
"In** has a more gradual slope at the beginning, making an animation move "
"slower at the beginning, and faster at the end. **Ease-In/Out (Back)** has a "
"gradual beginning and ending, but actually goes past the expected value and "
"then back (producing a bounce effect)."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan kurva Bézier untuk animasi, OpenShot menyertakan lebih dari "
"20 preset kurva (yang memengaruhi bentuk kurva). Misalnya, **Ease-In** "
"memiliki kemiringan yang lebih bertahap di awal, membuat animasi bergerak "
"lebih lambat di awal, dan lebih cepat di akhir. **Ease-In/Out (Back)** "
"memiliki awal dan akhir yang bertahap, tetapi sebenarnya melewati nilai yang "
"diharapkan dan kemudian kembali (menghasilkan efek pantulan)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:103
msgid ""
"To choose a curve preset, right click on the small graph icon next to a key "
"frame."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih preset kurva, klik kanan pada ikon grafik kecil di sebelah key "
"frame."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:110
msgid "Image Sequences"
msgstr "Urutan Gambar"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you have a sequence of similarly named images (such as, cat001.png, "
"cat002.png, cat003.png, etc...), you can simply drag and drop one of them "
"into OpenShot, and you will be prompted to import the entire sequence. "
"OpenShot will playback these sequential images rapidly, as if they are "
"frames in a video. The rate or speed in which these images are displayed is "
"based on their frame rate."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memiliki urutan gambar dengan nama yang serupa (seperti cat001."
"png, cat002.png, cat003.png, dll...), Anda dapat menyeret dan melepaskan "
"salah satunya ke OpenShot, dan Anda akan diminta untuk mengimpor seluruh "
"urutan. OpenShot akan memutar gambar-gambar berurutan ini dengan cepat, "
"seolah-olah mereka adalah frame dalam video. Kecepatan atau laju tampilan "
"gambar-gambar ini didasarkan pada frame rate-nya."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:116
msgid ""
"**NOTE:** Be sure your image sequence starts at 0 or 1, or you will likely "
"receive an error when importing it into OpenShot. For example, if your "
"sequence starts at cat222.png, or has missing images in the sequence, "
"OpenShot will struggle to understand the sequence. An easy work-around is to "
"renumber the images so they start with 1."
msgstr ""
"**CATATAN:** Pastikan urutan gambar Anda dimulai dari 0 atau 1, atau Anda "
"kemungkinan akan menerima kesalahan saat mengimpornya ke OpenShot. Misalnya, "
"jika urutan Anda dimulai dari cat222.png, atau ada gambar yang hilang dalam "
"urutan, OpenShot akan kesulitan memahami urutan tersebut. Solusi mudah "
"adalah memberi nomor ulang gambar sehingga dimulai dari 1."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:122
msgid ""
"To adjust the frame rate of the animation, right click and choose **File "
"Properties** in the **Project Files** panel, and adjust the frame rate. Once "
"you have set the correct frame rate, drag the animation onto the timeline."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur frame rate animasi, klik kanan dan pilih **File Properties** "
"di panel **Project Files**, lalu atur frame rate-nya. Setelah Anda mengatur "
"frame rate yang benar, seret animasi ke timeline."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
