msgid "File Properties"
msgstr "Properti Berkas"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:133
msgid ""
"Select an image sequence in the **Project Files** panel, right click and "
"choose **File Properties**"
msgstr ""
"Pilih urutan gambar di panel **Project Files**, klik kanan dan pilih **File "
