msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "Frame Rate"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:134
msgid ""
"Adjust the frame rate of the animation. Typically, hand-drawn animations use "
"12 frames per second."
msgstr ""
"Atur frame rate animasi. Biasanya, animasi gambar tangan menggunakan 12 "
"frame per detik."
